sentences: The Secretariat noted minor budgetary and administrative implications of the SBI outcomes.
The SBI then adopted its report on the session (FCCC/SBI/2008/L.15).
Reflecting on the session, Chair Asadi said the formal outcome left much to be desired, due in part to lack of time.
However, he also noted some positive outcomes, including a modest but encouraging start to the joint contact group on Protocol Articles 2.3 and 3.14.
He urged a collective endeavor to find common solutions to our common problems, and closed the meeting at 9:02 pm.
